Link LAPACKE in C
-----------------

This example shows to link LAPACKE in C code. LAPACKE and CBLAS are the C 
extensions to LAPACK and BLAS. One should additionally build LAPACKE and CBLAS 
when building LAPACK and BLAS. Once the compilation and installation done, add 
the path to LAPACK to LAPACK_HOME in CMakeLists.txt. To build the code, run
$ mkdir build && cd build
$ cmake ..